{"tid":1582376,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"【餅卷兌換行動】麻煩同我入晒黎！！！","createTime":"2019-09-20T04:37:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T08:38:21.000Z","uid":258830,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"273e76a6a2497269d74a701aab7700501f980ffc","tid":1582376,"uid":258830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T04:37:21.000Z","msg":"【1】<br />\n既然手上堆餅卡遲早要換。<br />\n咁當然係物盡其用！反正錢都預支左比佢&hellip;<br />\n定係你想留住佢過世呢？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-----------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n【2】<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>點解集中買西餅？</strong></span><br />\n麵包佢正常係日日清，無人買就日日蝕，整一個蝕一個！ <br />\n而 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">西餅係可存放得耐過麵包</span></strong>！<br />\n亦係除麵包外，主要現金流嘅來源！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當有班餅卷債主，拎堆廢紙黎換走晒佢堆貨&hellip;<br />\n佢係直接全日無野賣，只收到一疊疊廢紙&hellip;<br />\n變相收銀機無收過現金，全日營業額就會消失！ <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n比著你係客&hellip;<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">尋日買唔到，今日你會補買番尋日條數？<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"></span></strong></span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">除非你真係好鐘意食西餅，唔食會死 </span></span>&hellip; <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n平時你換西餅，唔多人換時，佢每日總會賣剩！<br />\n變相你拎少量餅卡去換，變相就係幫佢清貨尾 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n對佢黎講餅卡從來唔係錢！而係債券！<br />\n佢早就拎晒你買餅卡筆錢去投資！<br />\n到你換餅就當還債&hellip;你最好唔黎追債！唔換餅！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-----------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n【3】<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>點解盡量唔好預訂蛋糕？</strong></span><br />\n預訂蛋糕佢係靠工場整<br />\n佢一話單多，要等多幾日&hellip; <br />\n條款上，你落單佢同你講要遲幾日先有，消委會都幫你唔到！<br />\n簡單講，你吹佢唔脹！ <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢只要將你堆預訂，打散成幾日工場 Quota 就完事&hellip;<br />\n工場一日整到幾多，你認為佢心中無數？ <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n爆 Quota 就唔做，唔接單囉&hellip;<br />\n你唔係認為佢會專登請人 OT 去整你個蛋糕掛？？<br />\n咁你認為預訂蛋糕，對佢有乜影響？？？<br />\n受影響嘅，大概就只有聽日生日，今日先黎訂蛋糕毫無誠意嘅人 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-----------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n【4】<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>換唔換現成蛋糕好？</strong></span><br />\n因為現成蛋糕係一個個百幾二百蚊咁買，並唔係人人會買&hellip;<br />\n呢堆其實都算係罷買目標！<br />\n佢無可能唔整，但一整無人買，一蝕係蝕整個蛋糕！<br />\n但由於都係放雪櫃，可以放足幾日，可拖長售賣期&hellip;<br />\n所以都可以考慮清埋佢！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n-----------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n【5】<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">買餅位置要留意！</span></strong><br />\n唔好搵門面，設有廚房工場個種舖！<br />\n否則佢好大機會補得到貨！<br />\n相反，尤其地鐵站個堆就，等運到喇你<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n-----------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n麵包日日整、日日蝕&hellip;<br />\n西餅、現成蛋糕就比債券換走晒&hellip;<br />\n單日，甚至多日商舖銷售額歸零！<br />\n現金流嘅野&hellip;我真係唔識&hellip;<br />\n <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">尋日買唔到，今日你會補買番尋日條數嗎？</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\"><strong>兄弟爬山，各自努力！</strong></span></span></strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"337ad44b18bc771a33b8daad0d8c17b763315702","tid":1582376,"uid":258830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T04:38:22.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n01/10"},{"pid":"79adadeba11811dd9f24d12009a42a3672f6819d","tid":1582376,"uid